entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Brigitte pap renmen sa a ditou." t="Brigitte won't like this one bit." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Depi ki lè li oblije konnen?" t="And since when was she supposed to know about it?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou panse manzè se yon Danbala ki wè tout bagay?" t="You think she some Damballa dat see all?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Sa ou reproche manzè?" t="What you have against her?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Manzè se tout moun, li pwoteje nou..." t="She cares about everyone, protects us..." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Fòk mwen di manzè tou lè mwen pral lan twalèt?" t="Should I inform her when I go take a shit, too?" b="" a=""/>
